4:16.000Z","msg":"米燈啦屌"},{"pid":"d06da132dc70941c9f785d49d5055bfb5d6bc542","tid":2474902,"uid":87073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8ccab004bc654e2869179e2a54664de55ec99f2","tid":2474902,"uid":89939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"271f4930d8d02f9479308d87cf96cbc8c15e6be3","tid":2474902,"uid":87073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e852f0ac40bd2eda016d02bb1568a880947946e","tid":2474902,"uid":23699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-10T18:46:15.000Z","msg":"點解咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T04:25:22.000Z","msg":"大升係要付對代價"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T06:21:22.000Z","msg":"咁BTC呢 係咪又落返去1皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T14:36:31.000Z","msg":"6位數去番5位"},{"pid":"83852fbe5c545a2c336a2e12d5d7df625f6f4e17","tid":2474902,"uid":108589,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c0957e96a8dea2e0d52988bb227f9482d05208d7","tid":2474902,"uid":334720,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0b13688d93baf0aa7a47ee4032560155c9e6701","tid":2474902,"uid":44513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c398cfb8bf488ef937f055620851ac791b04b45","tid":2474902,"uid":47001,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-04-10T05:05:27.000Z","msg":"有無試過宜家個機制去計，<br />\n如果eth值5000, 做一個txn要幾多錢？<br />\n<br />\nEth值錢因為DeFi 多人用<br />\n多人用network fee 就愈高<br />\nNetwork fee愈高就愈少人用<br />\n<br />\n其實係deadlock 左<br />\n<br />\n咁當然，eth 價值可係純炒作"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-10T07:20:43.000Z","msg":"你講呢個問題eth開發團隊都有注意到<br />\n最近Berlin 同黎講London兩個更新已經改善緊<br />\n<br />\n當然長遠就要等ETH 2.0了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T07:41:19.000Z","msg":"2.0唔係年頭出左啦咩？<br />\n<br />\n同埋見d片都係話eth係2nd gen, ada係3rd gen，有eth既features之餘仲要係改良版<br />\n<br />\n咁ada應該會有potential過eth?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T14:46:15.000Z","msg":"唔好聽人地講ada/dot 功能上會好過 eth，所以 eth 就沒落。講呢啲野既人，都唔係eth 用家或者 都唔係 programmer。只係吹水既炒友。<br />\n<br />\n 你幻想你打開 ps5，有一日強國騰訊出左部遊戲機話功能勁過 ps5，畫面靚啲，無咁 lag，係 ps5 既下一代。你做玩家會唔會狗衝過去買部機黎玩？你唔會，你會睇定啲先，睇下啲大作係咪真係係個度出先再決定。同樣，遊戲開發商都唔會因為騰訊出左部機，就將啲大作移植過去，因為個度根本就無玩家。平台效應係好難打破既野，仲要 ETH 係以冠絕其他平台既速度去進步，ADA/DOT/BNB 見到車尾燈都當你贏。"},{"pid":"d37bf07754f1745b3f99b9c30ddd36748c988ce5","tid":2474902,"uid":47001,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1531e6f775eb7f7bd5c53dfabe123095a3e39de","tid":2474902,"uid":66004,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c398cfb8bf488ef937f055620851ac791b04b45","tid":2474902,"uid":47001,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-04-10T05:05:27.000Z","msg":"有無試過宜家個機制去計，<br />\n如果eth值5000, 做一個txn要幾多錢？<br />\n<br />\nEth值錢因為DeFi 多人用<br />\n多人用network fee 就愈高<br />\nNetwork fee愈高就愈少人用<br />\n<br />\n其實係deadlock 左<br />\n<br />\n咁當然，eth 價值可係純炒作"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T06:13:13.000Z","msg":"少人用左 又會平返d<br />\n唔明點deadlock<br />\n<br />\nNetwork fee 貴係問題<br />\n但就係貴都咁多人用<br />\n<br />\n一個 network 同一盤生意一樣<br />\n點都會有物理上限<br />\n一間餐廳收 $100,000 一位都好<br />\n如果都係(/接近)爆場<br />\n佢就唔需要諗點樣平d 多d人afford到<br />\n而係諗點樣做到多d生意 eg. 分店, 加位, 請多d chefs"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T16:35:34.000Z","msg":"Deadlock 係講緊個頂，回落已經係release 番個lock  <br />\n<br />\n加位=加block gas limit = bch=治標唔治本<br />\n<br />\n分店=sharding, 太長遠同有cross shard 問題<br />\n<br />\n短期最可靠得L2, 但L2 user 其實唔駛用eth 做fee"},{"pid":"beaba75981d7ab4dbaa25c5c3d38b55fed17804b","tid":2474902,"uid":57480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T16:40:33.000Z","msg":"ETH 要等<br />\ngas free 問題解決到嘅話<br />\n好多 coin 都收皮"},{"pid":"6694f1be50fc27b71e2ccb225a552125230b2e41","tid":2474902,"uid":127727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T16:44:08.000Z","msg":"drop to zero la"},{"pid":"c64bf51bbcfeb8f7c00f3b3011d8742866133ebe","tid":2474902,"uid":6030,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T08:19:37.000Z","msg":"睇返呢度嘅負評，證明連登仔嘅燈力根本勁過腦燒<img src=\"/assets/fac